{"tid":771054,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"就24，夢想48歲過退休生活，你問我答","createTime":"2018-08-07T15:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T15:28:42.000Z","uid":147241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59265f02ac3a111e72b027f49d5b2879402a1809","tid":771054,"uid":147241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b1fd12c27d4248f125294597f250953f062a09","tid":771054,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:22:31.000Z","msg":"失業真係好Q正<br />\n<br />\n每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"a0b44e8d7be0f99d84906eeaf1ed28243762e2c3","tid":771054,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:24:06.000Z","msg":"早d訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8f70ed7224e843bcd826de8017edf5af9e59df","tid":771054,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"人工幾多"},{"pid":"e35e68e8f65f449e239419a787b1f9f8a044dec3","tid":771054,"uid":147241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8f70ed7224e843bcd826de8017edf5af9e59df","tid":771054,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"人工幾多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"皮鬆"},{"pid":"f5f2e09a8ee2f414937956fc9b8c423d24735650","tid":771054,"uid":147241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b44e8d7be0f99d84906eeaf1ed28243762e2c3","tid":771054,"uid":37599,"like":0,"